    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small oval cups that have a rim curved to fit the orbit of the eye. Used to bathe the eye or for applying liquid remedies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
